\newlabel{fig:rose_results}{{3}{5}{Rose/UBER system: comprehensive ML comparison. (a)~Data efficiency showing $R^2$ versus training set size. (b)~$R^2$ across interpolation and extrapolation test regimes. (c)~Noise robustness. (d)~Example extrapolation prediction. (e)~Parameter prediction quality (extrapolation). See text for details}{figure.3}{}}
